    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The wood of the evergreen tree Hippomane mancinella, found in the Caribbean; although the tree is highly poisonous, the wood takes a good polish and is sometimes used in furniture.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
